node.text: Truly the sweetest guys & best dads. So thankful for my own dad and how he’s loved and supported me and cared for me so deeply. Then for John Luke and the incredible dad he is to our two little ones- so fun and helpful and steady. Just the best. And also my father-in-law who is so dependable and cooks the best food. Really grateful for these fathers who love Jesus and love our family and I count it one of the greatest blessings.
